					Entdecke Georgien
				</h1>
				<div
					class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 text-center bg-[#353849]"
				>
					<!-- Card 1 -->
					<div
						class="bg-gray-800 rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden"
					>
						<iframe
							class="border-[2px] ml-auto mr-auto  mt-7 rounded-lg"
